Package a2

Class Student

java.lang.Object
a2.Student
Direct Known Subclasses:
Student_Course, Student_Research
public class Student extends Object
The 'Student' class is a Super class for sub classes of Student_Course and Student_Research. It lays the foundation of the basic information of a Student and the main grounds of the program. This class will be further developed further in its subclasses.

NOTE: This class is not meant to be instantiated on its own, but rather as a parent class for its sub classes.

Author:
yeojustin
